  "page": "Whore (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>whore</b> is a person who receives payment for sexual services through <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">prostitution</a>. Other usages include:\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Whore_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Harroway\" title=\"Alys Harroway\">Alys Harroway</a>, known as Maegor's Whore</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellaria_Sand\" title=\"Ellaria Sand\">Ellaria Sand</a>, known as the serpent's whore</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Herrock_Kenning\" title=\"Herrock Kenning\">Herrock Kenning</a>, known as Herrock the Whoreson</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hother_Umber\" title=\"Hother Umber\">Hother Umber</a>, known as Whoresbane</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maerie_the_Whore\" title=\"Maerie the Whore\">Maerie the Whore</a>, an inhabitant of the riverlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Whore\" title=\"Queen Whore\">Queen Whore</a>, the concubine of Cleon the Second</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Queen_o%27_whores\" title=\"Queen o&#39; whores\">Queen o' whores</a>, a camp follower servicing Ser Ryman Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a>, referred to by her enemies as the whore of Dragonstone</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Silver-haired_whore\" title=\"Silver-haired whore\">Silver-haired whore</a> in Selhorys</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Widow_of_the_waterfront\" title=\"Widow of the waterfront\">Widow of the waterfront</a>, referred to by the Old Blood of Volantis as Vogarro's whore</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Others\">Others</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Whore_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Others\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Whore_(weapon)\" title=\"Whore (weapon)\">Whore (weapon)</a>, an torture tool at the Wolf's Den</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Three_Whores\" title=\"Three Whores\">Three Whores</a>, three great trebuchets in King's Landing</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a>, rudely referred to as the Kingdom of the Three Whores</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Whore%27s_Barrow\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whore&#39;s Barrow\">Whore's Barrow</a>, a recent nickname for Long Barrow</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Whore%27s_Gash\" title=\"Whore&#39;s Gash\">Whore's Gash</a>, a pirate lair in the Basilisk Isles</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403190323\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 7/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:31137-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403190323 and revision id 326671\n -->\n",
